Package: saeproj.multilevel
Type: Package
Title: Small Area Estimation via Projection Estimator with Linear Multilevel Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nazlya", "Rahma Susanto",
    email = "susantonazlya@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for small area estimation using a projection
    estimator approach with linear mixed-effects working models. The main
    function sae_ml_linear() fits a linear multilevel model on a smaller model
    survey, generates synthetic predictions on a larger projection survey, and
    aggregates predictions to domain-level estimates using survey design
    information. Both synthetic and bias-corrected estimators are supported.
